iant Enron (ENE <http://tscquote.thestreet.com/StockQuotes.jhtml?tkr=3DENE>:=
NYSE) on Tuesday, </funds/chrisedmonds/1518235.html> for what he would only =
say were "personal reasons." While Enron's stock performance since Skilling =
ascended to the CEO spot in February has left shareholders wanting, his depa=
rture is being assailed by many as both selfish and riddling.=20
