ling in 1997. Skilling repaid $2 million in 1999 and his employment contract=
 calls for the balance of the loan to be forgiven "if Mr. Skilling fulfills =
all the duties and responsibilities under his employment agreement through D=
ec. 31, 2001 or is involuntarily terminated prior to Dec. 31, 2001."=20
